&amp;_svg]:size-4 md:px-6\" data-toc-popover-trigger=\"\"><svg role=\"progressbar\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-valuenow=\"0\" aria-valuemin=\"0\" aria-valuemax=\"1\" class=\"shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" class=\"stroke-current/25\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-dasharray=\"69.11503837897544\" stroke-dashoffset=\"69.11503837897544\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" transform=\"rotate(-90 12 12)\" class=\"transition-all\"></circle></svg><span class=\"grid flex-1 *:my-auto *:row-start-1 *:col-start-1\"><span class=\"truncate transition-[opacity,translate,color]\">Dashboard</span><span class=\"truncate transition-[opacity,translate] opacity-0 translate-y-full pointer-events-none\"></span></span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down shrink-0 transition-transform mx-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button><div data-state=\"closed\" id=\"radix-_R_1av5u9flb_\" hidden=\"\" data-toc-popover-content=\"\" class=\"overflow-hidden\"></div></header></div><article id=\"nd-page\" data-full=\"false\" class=\"flex flex-col w-full max-w-[900px] mx-auto [grid-area:main] px-4 py-6 gap-4 md:px-6 md:pt-8 xl:px-8 xl:pt-14 xl:layout:[--fd-toc-width:268px]\"><h1 class=\"text-[1.75em] font-semibold\">Dashboard</h1><p class=\"text-lg text-fd-muted-foreground mb-0\">A real-time overview of your salon&#x27;s performance — revenue, appointments, and top staff</p><div class=\"flex flex-row gap-2 items-center border-b pb-6\"><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md p-2 font-medium transition-colors duration-100 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-fd-ring border bg-fd-secondary text-fd-secondary-foreground hover:bg-fd-accent hover:text-fd-accent-foreground px-2 py-1.5 text-xs gap-2 [&amp;_svg]:size-3.5 [&amp;_svg]:text-fd-muted-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-copy\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"14\" height=\"14\" x=\"8\" y=\"8\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2\"></path></svg>Copy Markdown</button><button type=\"button\" aria-haspopup=\"dialog\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"radix-_R_9qav5u9flb_\" data-state=\"closed\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md p-2 font-medium transition-colors duration-100 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-fd-ring border bg-fd-secondary text-fd-secondary-foreground hover:bg-fd-accent hover:text-fd-accent-foreground px-2 py-1.5 text-xs gap-2 data-[state=open]:bg-fd-accent data-[state=open]:text-fd-accent-foreground\">Open<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down size-3.5 text-fd-muted-foreground\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"prose flex-1\"><p>The Dashboard is the first thing you see when you log in as an admin. It gives you a quick, up-to-date picture of how your salon is performing — without having to dig through reports or spreadsheets.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Dashboard Overview\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"rounded-lg\" style=\"color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, (max-width: 1200px) 70vw, 900px\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F0_dashboard.09f87--t_h2ja.gif&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F0_dashboard.09f87--t_h2ja.gif&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F0_dashboard.09f87--t_h2ja.gif&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F0_dashboard.09f87--t_h2ja.gif&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F0_dashboard.09f87--t_h2ja.gif&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F0_dashboard.09f87--t_h2ja.gif&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F0_dashboard.09f87--t_h2ja.gif&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F0_dashboard.09f87--t_h2ja.gif&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F0_dashboard.09f87--t_h2ja.gif&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></p>\n<div class=\"flex gap-2 my-4 rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-3 ps-1 text-sm text-fd-card-foreground shadow-md\" style=\"--callout-color:var(--color-fd-info, var(--color-fd-muted))\"><div role=\"none\" class=\"w-0.5 bg-(--callout-color)/50 rounded-sm\"></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-info size-5 -me-0.5 fill-(--callout-color) text-fd-card\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 16v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 8h.01\"></path></svg><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 min-w-0 flex-1\"><div class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"><p>The Dashboard is only visible to admin users.</p></div></div></div>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"filtering-by-date-range\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#filtering-by-date-range\" class=\"peer\">Filtering by Date Range</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>At the top of the Dashboard is the <strong>Filter by Date Range</strong> bar. By default the dashboard shows recent data, but you can narrow it down to any period you want.</p>\n<div class=\"fd-steps\"><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Click <strong>Show Calendar</strong> on the right side of the filter bar. A two-month calendar picker will appear.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Click a <strong>start date</strong>, then click an <strong>end date</strong>. The selected range will be highlighted between the two dates.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>The entire Dashboard updates automatically to reflect only that period.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Click <strong>Hide Calendar</strong> to close the picker when you&#x27;re done.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"flex gap-2 my-4 rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-3 ps-1 text-sm text-fd-card-foreground shadow-md\" style=\"--callout-color:var(--color-fd-info, var(--color-fd-muted))\"><div role=\"none\" class=\"w-0.5 bg-(--callout-color)/50 rounded-sm\"></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-info size-5 -me-0.5 fill-(--callout-color) text-fd-card\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 16v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 8h.01\"></path></svg><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 min-w-0 flex-1\"><div class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"><p>Use the <strong>&lt;</strong> and <strong>&gt;</strong> arrows on the calendar to navigate to earlier or later months.</p></div></div></div>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"sales-by-location\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#sales-by-location\" class=\"peer\">Sales by Location</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>A donut chart showing total revenue broken down by location. Below the chart you&#x27;ll see the grand total and how many locations are currently active.</p>\n<p>This gives you an instant feel for which branches are driving the most revenue — especially useful if you run multiple locations.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"payment-methods\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#payment-methods\" class=\"peer\">Payment Methods</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>A donut chart right next to Sales by Location, showing how your revenue was collected — broken down by payment method (Cash, Card, Online, Membership, etc.).</p>\n<p>Below the chart, each payment method is listed with its exact total for the period. Use this to see whether clients prefer paying by card or cash, or to verify totals against your till at the end of the day.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"recent-sales\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#recent-sales\" class=\"peer\">Recent Sales</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p><strong>All locations · Last 7 days</strong></p>\n<p>A summary card showing:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Total revenue</strong> collected over the last 7 days</li>\n<li><strong>Number of appointments</strong> completed</li>\n<li><strong>Appointments value</strong> — the combined price of all booked services</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Below the numbers, a <strong>line chart</strong> tracks revenue and appointment count day by day so you can spot your busiest days and see whether bookings are translating into actual sales.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"upcoming-appointments\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#upcoming-appointments\" class=\"peer\">Upcoming Appointments</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p><strong>All locations · Next 7 days</strong></p>\n<p>A summary card showing what&#x27;s on the books:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Total appointments booked</li>\n<li>How many are <strong>confirmed</strong></li>\n<li>How many have been <strong>cancelled</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>A <strong>bar chart</strong> breaks this down day by day — great for spotting gaps in the schedule or flagging a day that has an unusually high cancellation rate.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"appointments-activity\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#appointments-activity\" class=\"peer\">Appointments Activity</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>A live feed of the most recent appointment events across all your locations — new bookings, updates, checkouts, and cancellations. Each entry shows the date, time, service, client (or Walk-In), duration, and which staff member is assigned.</p>\n<p>This is your go-to for staying on top of last-minute changes, especially if you&#x27;re managing more than one location.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"todays-next-appointments\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#todays-next-appointments\" class=\"peer\">Today&#x27;s Next Appointments</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>A list of the remaining appointments for today, sorted by time. Each entry shows:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The appointment time</li>\n<li>The service being performed</li>\n<li>The client&#x27;s name (or Walk-In)</li>\n<li>The staff member handling it</li>\n<li>The status badge (e.g., <strong>Booked</strong>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Use this for a quick check of what&#x27;s still to come in the day.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"top-services\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#top-services\" class=\"peer\">Top Services</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>A table showing which services are being booked the most, ranked by volume.</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Column</th><th>What it shows</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Service</td><td>The name of the treatment</td></tr><tr><td>This month</td><td>How many times it was booked this month</td></tr><tr><td>Last month</td><td>Last month&#x27;s count for comparison</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"flex gap-2 my-4 rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-3 ps-1 text-sm text-fd-card-foreground shadow-md\" style=\"--callout-color:var(--color-fd-info, var(--color-fd-muted))\"><div role=\"none\" class=\"w-0.5 bg-(--callout-color)/50 rounded-sm\"></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-info size-5 -me-0.5 fill-(--callout-color) text-fd-card\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 16v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 8h.01\"></path></svg><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 min-w-0 flex-1\"><div class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"><p>Click on any service name to jump straight to that service in your Catalog.</p></div></div></div>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"top-team-members\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#top-team-members\" class=\"peer\">Top Team Members</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>A table ranking your staff by total sales for the selected month. You can search by name and filter by month and year.</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Column</th><th>What it shows</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Team member</td><td>Staff member&#x27;s name</td></tr><tr><td>This month</td><td>Total sales value for the current month</td></tr><tr><td>Last month</td><td>Last month&#x27;s total for comparison</td></tr><tr><td>Actions</td><td>Generate a salary slip for that team member</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>The <strong>Actions</strong> column has a salary slip icon — click it to open a formatted breakdown of that person&#x27;s services, commission, and total payout for the period.</p>\n<p>You can also export the full table using the <strong>CSV</strong>, <strong>Excel</strong>, or <strong>PDF</strong> buttons in the top-right corner.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"commission-calculations\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#commission-calculations\" class=\"peer\">Commission Calculations</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>At the bottom of the Dashboard is the <strong>Commission Calculations</strong> widget. It shows a live summary of what each staff member has earned in commission for the selected month.</p>\n<p>At the top of the widget you&#x27;ll see four summary numbers:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Team Members</strong> — how many staff have sales this period</li>\n<li><strong>Total Sales</strong> — combined revenue across all staff</li>\n<li><strong>Total Commission</strong> — total commission owed</li>\n<li><strong>Avg Commission %</strong> — average commission rate across the team</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Below that, the table shows each team member with:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Their number of sales</li>\n<li>Their total sales value</li>\n<li>Their commission type (or <strong>No Setup</strong> if commission hasn&#x27;t been configured yet)</li>\n<li>Their commission rate and calculated amount</li>\n<li>An eye icon to view their breakdown and a salary slip icon to generate their slip</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Filter by month and year using the dropdowns at the top of the widget. The date range being shown is displayed at the bottom of the table.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"dashboard-overview\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#dashboard-overview\" class=\"peer\">Dashboard Overview</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Section</th><th>What it tells you</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Date range filter</td><td>Narrow all dashboard data to any period</td></tr><tr><td>Sales by Location</td><td>Revenue breakdown by branch</td></tr><tr><td>Payment Methods</td><td>How revenue was collected (cash, card, online, etc.)</td></tr><tr><td>Recent Sales</td><td>Last 7 days revenue with a daily trend chart</td></tr><tr><td>Upcoming Appointments</td><td>Next 7 days bookings — confirmed vs. cancelled</td></tr><tr><td>Appointments Activity</td><td>Live feed of the latest appointment events</td></tr><tr><td>Today&#x27;s Next Appointments</td><td>What&#x27;s still happening today</td></tr><tr><td>Top Services</td><td>Most booked services this month vs. last</td></tr><tr><td>Top Team Members</td><td>Top earners with salary slip and export</td></tr><tr><td>Commission Calculations</td><td>Monthly commission summary per staff member</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"@container grid gap-4 grid-cols-2\"><a class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-lg border p-4 text-sm transition-colors hover:bg-fd-accent/80 hover:text-fd-accent-foreground @max-lg:col-span-full\" href=\"/docs\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-left -mx-1 size-4 shrink-0 rtl:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m15 18-6-6 6-6\"></path></svg><p>Welcome to NxCut</p></div><p class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground truncate\">Everything you need to run your salon — bookings, payments, staff, and more</p></a><a class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-lg border p-4 text-sm transition-colors hover:bg-fd-accent/80 hover:text-fd-accent-foreground @max-lg:col-span-full text-end\" href=\"/docs/calendar\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium flex-row-reverse\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right -mx-1 size-4 shrink-0 rtl:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg><p>Calendar &amp; Bookings</p></div><p class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground truncate\">Book, view, and manage all your salon appointments in one place</p></a></div></article><div id=\"nd-toc\" class=\"sticky top-(--fd-docs-row-1) h-[calc(var(--fd-docs-height)-var(--fd-docs-row-1))] flex flex-col [grid-area:toc] w-(--fd-toc-width) pt-12 pe-4 pb-2 max-xl:hidden\"><h3 id=\"toc-title\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-text-align-start size-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21 5H3\"></path><path d=\"M15 12H3\"></path><path d=\"M17 19H3\"></path></svg>On this page</h3><div class=\"relative min-h-0 text-sm ms-px overflow-auto [scrollbar-width:none] mask-[linear-gradient(to_bottom,transparent,white_16px,white_calc(100%-16px),transparent)] py-3\"><div class=\"relative\"><div data-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-y-0 inset-s-0 bg-fd-primary w-px transition-[clip-path]\" style=\"clip-path:polygon(0 var(--fd-top), 100% var(--fd-top), 100% calc(var(--fd-top) + var(--fd-height)), 0 calc(var(--fd-top) + var(--fd-height)))\"></div><div class=\"flex flex-col border-s border-fd-foreground/10\"><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#filtering-by-date-range\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Filtering by Date Range</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#sales-by-location\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Sales by Location</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#payment-methods\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Payment Methods</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#recent-sales\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Recent Sales</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#upcoming-appointments\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Upcoming Appointments</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#appointments-activity\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Appointments Activity</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#todays-next-appointments\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Today&#x27;s Next Appointments</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#top-services\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Top Services</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#top-team-members\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Top Team Members</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#commission-calculations\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Commission Calculations</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#dashboard-overview\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Dashboard Overview</a></div></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0ivik3ip_mfgc.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[67028,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0_b-80nser09y.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/02xrdmooo78xa.js\\\",\\\"/_next/st